title: Biochemical Engineering - James M. Lee
description:
Biochemical Engineering - James M. Lee (WSU, 2009).pdf

This book is written for an introductory course in biochemical engineering normally taught as a senior or graduate-level elective in chemical engineering. It is also intended to be used as a self-study book for practicing chemical engineers or for biological scientists who have a limited background in the bioprocessing aspects of new biotechnology
